<plot>A trashed and crowded beach with stressed out city people place is magically visited by a colorful "Healing Tribe." Without using words, these peaceful people create a circle, celebrating ancient rhythms and dances, inviting everyone to participate in the "Keep It Clean" experience. The whole beach crowd becomes part of a joyful environmental transformation, restoring the sands and water to a more natural state.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?288860</url></doc>
